{"tid":1621003,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[另一戰線］所有中小學家長唔好簽蒙面法通告回條","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:52:26.000Z","uid":73959,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c29d100b107113550f3da6982a8c74d3d12d47b","tid":1621003,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4MS9PG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4MS9PG.jpg&h=09d07375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因就係咁簡單<br />\n一定預咗會有老師強迫學生交返去<br />\n所有中小學生只需要講一句：要簽你直接搵我老母簽<br />\n然後所有家長都唔好簽！<br />\n政治唔應該岀現喺校園<br />\n咁呢張通告更加唔洗簽！<br />\n一簽即係你妥協<br />\n從此校園就變成打壓對象<br />\n愛你仔女就唔好簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68bedfadfb5e8a85ed8301e75558a36a6773e7b","tid":1621003,"uid":67168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"簽左 = endorse<br />\n我明家長好多時未必出到去 但你簽少左張回條 就幫緊呢場運動<br />\n<br />\n推比所有家長見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdee5647f5ff6ebe70c64a5c6d2b75cbc446204","tid":1621003,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔支持中學生去抗爭<br />\n就由家長去保護佢哋<br />\n你身為家長 應該要做個好榜樣<br />\n唔敢上前唔敢發夢唔緊要<br />\n呢張通告一定唔可以簽！<br />\n全部同我撕爛佢</span>"},{"pid":"2f84aa299210dec38ab2d22d27389ec4b085b525","tid":1621003,"uid":242110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26e19e557e885bee9d72e1867df868705c20cbfc","tid":1621003,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"所有中小學生：我老竇老母唔肯簽！<br />\n所有家長：我唔撚簽！<br />\n<br />\n冇人可以迫害學生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong